Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu: wait for moving fence after pinning
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 8ddf5b9bb479570a3825d70fecfb9399bc15700c
